11 An Act relating to the Oklahoma Public Employees
Retirement System; amending 62 O.S. 2021, Section
12 3103, as last amended by Section 2, Chapter 361,
O.S.L. 2024 (62 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 3103), which
13 relates to the Oklahoma Pension Legislation Actuarial
Analysis Act; modifying certain definition;
14 authorizing benefit increase for certain retired
members of the Oklahoma Public Employees Retirement
15 System; updating statutory language; providing for
codification; and providing effective dates.
16
17
18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
19 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 62 O.S. 2021, Section 3103, as
20 last amended by Section 2, Chapter 361, O.S.L. 2024 (62 O.S. Supp.
21 2025, Section 3103), is amended to read as follows:
22 Section 3103. As used in the Oklahoma Pension Legislation
23 Actuarial Analysis Act:
24
